                     java.io.File file)
        Parameters:
        modrinthModId - The id of your mod
        file_parts - An array of the multipart field names of each file that goes with this version
        version_number - A string that describes this version; should be something similar to semver, but isn't require to have a specific format
        version_title - The human readable name of the version
        version_body - A description of the version
        dependencies - A list of dependencies of this version; this must be specified as an array of version ids of other mods' versions
        game_versions - A list of game versions that this version supports
        releaseChannel - What type of release that this version is; release, beta, or alpha ReleaseChannel
        loaders - An array of the mod loaders that this mod supports Loaders
        featured - Whether the version should be featured on the mod's homepage
        file - The jar of your mod
